FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1778256667
OL,3,CBirthday tribute to Sir David
OL,4,CAttenborough displayed on Piccadilly
OL,5,CLights
OL,7,FThe message will be displayed
OL,8,Fthroughout the day and consists of a
OL,9,Ftwo-minute video by BBC Studios
OL,10,Fdedicated to Sir David from planet
OL,11,FEarth, reflecting on his decades-long
OL,12,Fcareer.
OL,14,FThe tribute emphasises his
OL,15,Fcontribution to natural history
OL,16,Ffilmmaking and storytelling using
OL,17,Farchival footage of Sir David, as well
OL,18,Fas clips from his recent work.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1778256667
OL,3,CBirthday tribute to Sir David
OL,4,CAttenborough displayed on Piccadilly
OL,5,CLights
OL,7,FThe video is said to "capture the
OL,8,Fspirit that defines his career and
OL,9,Finspires audiences", while reflecting
OL,10,Fon his key moments as a veteran
OL,11,Fbroadcaster and natural historian.
OL,13,FJonny Keeling, head of BBC Studios
OL,14,Fnatural history unit, said: "Sir David
OL,15,FAttenborough has changed the way we
OL,16,Fview the planet. He has inspired me
OL,17,Fand millions of others to love and
OL,18,Fcherish the natural world.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1778256667
OL,3,CBirthday tribute to Sir David
OL,4,CAttenborough displayed on Piccadilly
OL,5,CLights
OL,7,F"As he turns 100, this birthday
OL,8,Fmessage celebrates his extraordinary
OL,9,Fwork which continues to move audiences
OL,10,Fof all ages across the globe."
OL,12,FSir David said in a recorded audio
OL,13,Fmessage shared the night before his
OL,14,Fbirthday that he was "completely
OL,15,Foverwhelmed" by the birthday greetings
OL,16,Fand that he thought it would be
OL,17,Fcelebrated quietly.
OL,26,@vD@VOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
