PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1778256667
OL,3,CBirthday tribute to Sir David
OL,4,CAttenborough displayed on Piccadilly
OL,5,CLights
OL,7,FHe said: "I simply can't reply to each
OL,8,Fof you all separately but I would like
OL,9,Fto thank you all most sincerely for
OL,10,Fyour kind messages.
OL,12,F"I wish those of you who have planned
OL,13,Fyour own local events tomorrow a very
OL,14,Fhappy day."
OL,16,FIn the week leading up to his
OL,17,Fbirthday, Sir David was inundated with
OL,18,Fgood wishes.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUvD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
