PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1778256667
OL,3,CBirthday tribute to Sir David
OL,4,CAttenborough displayed on Piccadilly
OL,5,CLights
OL,7,FThe King and Queen shared a carousel
OL,8,Fof photographs of Sir David on the
OL,9,Fofficial royal family Instagram and X
OL,10,Faccounts.
OL,12,FThe caption read: "Wishing Sir David
OL,13,FAttenborough a very happy 100th
OL,14,Fbirthday.
OL,16,F"Enjoy your special celebration this
OL,17,Fevening!"
OL,26,@tD@SOUxD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
