FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1778256667
OL,3,CBirthday tribute to Sir David
OL,4,CAttenborough displayed on Piccadilly
OL,5,CLights
OL,7,FHis centenary is also being marked
OL,8,Fwith a live event at the Royal Albert
OL,9,FHall on Friday, featuring music from
OL,10,Fhis programmes along with stories and
OL,11,Freflections from public figures and
OL,12,Fleading advocates for the natural
OL,13,Fworld.
OL,15,FIt is just one of many events to mark
OL,16,Fhis birthday, as the Natural History
OL,17,FMuseum's immersive exhibition
OL,18,Fpresented by Sir David will be
OL,19,Ftransformed into a free five-minute
OL,20,Fshow in central London to celebrate.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
